{"tid":2018051,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"做project做到出晒冷汗","createTime":"2020-05-15T11:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T16:10:52.000Z","uid":157152,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9229cf18f78c013c76a5830a862286b7d4294f6b","tid":2018051,"uid":157152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"以前讀asso個時，同垃圾組員一齊做野，我會覺得好理所當然。<br />\n<br />\nI mean，我明架喇，level係咁上下，無得要求咁多。<br />\n<br />\n上返u之後，呢一年順風順水，百戰百勝，但係最近終於比我遇返呢類垃圾組員，臨deadline仲問人呢題點做個啲。<br />\n<br />\n係呢個時候，我個心突然間好寒，好恐慌，好似無晒寄託咁。<br />\n<br />\n我唔明點解我會咁，以前我都唔會咁驚，頂多carry下人，宜家我一諗起條友我就覺得自己落左地獄咁，好似撞邪咁，手都出晒冷汗。我唔明點解我會突然間比我見慣既垃圾嚇到賴屎，我宜家好混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c751cf288ae43e00bef341e69856b6985a6cf1c","tid":2018051,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:38:58.000Z","msg":"你咁叻點解當年會讀Asso?"},{"pid":"2539dc0010d2dde8f5b8f4a612fee90d5783833f","tid":2018051,"uid":157152,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"6c751cf288ae43e00bef341e69856b6985a6cf1c","tid":2018051,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:38:58.000Z","msg":"你咁叻點解當年會讀Asso?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"高中我都無心機讀書，女又無左，校長老師又換晒血，連學都唔想返，唔好話考高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw其實唔係我叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係啲人仲廢過我"},{"pid":"11f2388b18fc09aa3fb5aab42fd284499ae22f26","tid":2018051,"uid":33874,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:42:04.000Z","msg":"咁你會搞架啦<br />\n我坐等派grade咪得"},{"pid":"507c508535e58048cd7914920228ec54e94ae484","tid":2018051,"uid":157152,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f2388b18fc09aa3fb5aab42fd284499ae22f26","tid":2018051,"uid":33874,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:42:04.000Z","msg":"咁你會搞架啦<br />\n我坐等派grade咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim